JustinBieber-understands-turned-down-Super-Bowl-show-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/UsherJustinBieber-understands-turned-down-Super-Bowl-show-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/UsherJustinBieber-understands-turned-down-Super-Bowl-show-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/UsherJustinBieber-understands-turned-down-Super-Bowl-show-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/UsherJustinBieber-understands-turned-down-Super-Bowl-show-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/usher">亚瑟</a>小子表示，他“理解”<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justin-bieber">贾斯汀·比伯</a>为何拒绝在 2024 年超级碗上与他一起表演的邀请。</p><p> “是啊！”上周日（2 月 11 日），歌手在内华达州拉斯维加斯<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/usher-alicia-keys-super-bowl-halftime-show-performance-3585753">举行的今年中场秀中演奏了 13 分钟的混合曲目</a>。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alicia-keys">艾丽西亚·凯斯 (Alicia Keys)</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/h-e-r">HER</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/will-i-am">威廉 (Will.i.am)</a>等人也登上了舞台。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="265" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/ranking-the-10-best-super-bowl-halftime-shows-in-history-3394980"><b>历史上 10 场最佳超级碗中场表演排名</b></a></li></ul><p>活动之前，有传言称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-bieber-seen-in-las-vegas-amid-super-bowl-guest-appearance-rumours-3585682">比伯将成为亚瑟小子在超级碗演出前调侃的“重要嘉宾”之一</a>。</p><p> 2008 年，亚瑟小子将当时十几岁的歌手签入自己的唱片公司，在开启比伯的音乐生涯方面发挥了关键作用。他们还合作制作了后者 2010 年的热门单曲《Somebody To Love》。</p><p>然而，这位《对不起》明星并没有出现，后来有报道称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-why-justin-bieber-turned-down-joining-usher-at-the-super-bowl-3586634">他拒绝了，因为他“没有感觉”</a> 。一位消息人士称：“亚瑟小子和贾斯汀之间并没有什么不和。贾斯汀只是不愿意这么做——他只是没有感觉。”</p><p>在周一（2 月 19 日）即将发布的<em>《早餐俱乐部》</em>一集的一段剪辑中，亚瑟小子被问到为什么与比伯的现场合作没有成功。</p><p> “我很荣幸并认识到这一点，我的兄弟……我认为这可能是因为他现在只是想讲述一个不同的故事。我明白这一点，”他回答道。 “但我们确实进行了一次简短的交谈。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C3aeRtPLFF1/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.